\sphinxAtStartPar
Art\sphinxhyphen{}Snake helps artists to protect their work from theft. It is a simple and easy\sphinxhyphen{}to\sphinxhyphen{}use tool that allows artists to add a watermark,
both visible and invisible, to their digital art.
